0 REQUEST~
{138}
                                   Request
{300}
The request command temporarily changes game modes for the current session.

REQUEST V-     Temporarily turns off VT102 mode.
REQUEST V+     Turns VT102 back on after being temporarily disabled.
REQUEST C-     Temporarily turns off ansi color.
REQUEST C+     Turns ansi color back on after being temporarily disabled.

This could be useful for character sharing.
~

